    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but i'm seeing a lot of conflicting reports. some people are saying the supply-side effects like job creation and investment are going to naturally lift everyone up, while others are calling it a disaster for the middle class. which of those perspectives actually has more empirical backing in terms of long-term outcomes?",
